{# With title variant #}
<h3 id="title-header">With a title variant of header</h3>
<p>When developing a service you may not need the navigation of the main website. When this is the case, you can place the title of the service in the header (providing their is no other h1 element on the page).</p>

<p>To use the title variant:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Add the h1 element and ensure it has the classes <code class="ds-website-inline-code">.ds-header__title .ds-col-1 .ds-col-sm-auto</code> on the element</li>
</ul>


{{
  compExample([
    wmcadsHeaderV2({
      withTitle: true,
      title: "App title",
      legacyMenu: true,
      ds: ds
    })
  ], {
    componentPath: "wmcads/patterns/header-v2/",
    njk: false,
    js: true,
    iframe: true
  })
}}

